==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Ennui
<hw>En`nui"</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[F., fr. L.
<ets>in odio</ets> in hatred. See <er>Annoy</er>.]</ety> <def>A feeling
of weariness and disgust; dullness and languor of spirits, arising from
satiety or want of interest; tedium.</def> <rj><au>T.
Gray.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Ennuye</ent>⟦br⟧
